#: ../../C/cretin.rst:5
msgid "cretin"
msgstr "cretin"

#: ../../C/cretin.rst:7
msgid "/kret´in/, /kree´tn/, n\\."
msgstr "/kret´in/, /kree´tn/, 名詞"

#: ../../C/cretin.rst:9
msgid ""
"Congenital :ref:`loser`\\; an obnoxious person; someone who can't do "
"anything right. It has been observed that many American hackers tend to "
"favor the British pronunciation /kret´in/ over standard American /kree´tn/; "
"it is thought this may be due to the insidious phonetic influence of Monty "
"Python's Flying Circus."
msgstr ""
"生まれつきの\\ :ref:`loser`\\ "
"。不快な人。何一つまともにできない人。多くのアメリカ人ハッカーは、標準的なアメリカ式の/kree´tn/よりもイギリス式の発音/kret´in/を好む傾向があると観察されています。これはMonty"
" Python's Flying Circusの陰湿な音声的影響によるものかもしれないと考えられています。"
